ocal language of the country the ride is conducted in.</p>\n                </div>\n            </details>\n        \n    \n        \n            <details class=\"faq-item\">\n                <summary>Can I add child seats to the booking?</summary>\n                <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n                    <p>Yes, this is possible. Please select the Business Van/SUV vehicle class and add the required child seat in the “Notes for the chauffeur” field. We will do our best to organize a child seat ahead of time.</p>\n                </div>\n            </details>\n        \n    \n</section>\n\n\n\n    \n  </div>\n\n  </main>\n  \n<section id=\"footer\">\n  <footer style=\"background: url('/static/img/bg.webp') no-repeat center center/cover; color: white;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"row gy-4\">\n        <div class=\"col-lg-3 col-md-6 footer-logo\">\n          \n          <img src=\"/media/company/logo_03.png\" alt=\"Amhar Chauffeur Service\" title=\"Amhar Chauffeur Service\">\n          \n        </div>\n        <div class=\"col-lg-3 col-md-6 letterSpacing\">\n          <span class=\"footer-title text-white\">Contact Info</span>\n          <p>\n            <i class=\"fa fa-map-marker-alt me-2\"></i> Riyadh, Saudi Arabia<br>\n            <a href=\"mailto:booking@amharksa.com?subject=Inquiry\" class=\"text-decoration-none\">\n              <i class=\"fas fa-envelope me-2\"></i> booking@amharksa.com<br>\n            </a>\n            <a href=\"https://wa.me/966535674246\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"text-decoration-none\">\n              <i class=\"fas fa-phone me-2\"></i> +966 50 315 2119\n            </a>\n          </p>\n          <hr>\n          <span class=\"footer-title text-white\">Follow Us</span>\n          <div>\n            <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61579634004083\" aria-label=\"Follow us on Facebook\"><i class=\"fab fa-facebook-f me-3\"></i><span class=\"visually-hidden\">Follow us on Facebook</span></a>\n  